---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout title="Contenido RSS | Digitaliza Todo">
  <div class="min-h-screen py-32 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="mb-8">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-indigo-600 dark:hover:text-indigo-400 transition-colors">
          <i data-lucide="arrow-left" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
          Volver
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-12">
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-mono font-bold bg-pink-100 dark:bg-pink-900/30 text-pink-700 dark:text-pink-400 mb-4">Media</div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Contenido RSS</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-6">En redes sociales tienes 0.5 segundos para captar atención.</p>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-mono">$19.890</div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="p-3 rounded-xl bg-pink-100 dark:bg-pink-900/30 text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400">
              <i data-lucide="image" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Servicios incluidos</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-pink-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i><span>Diseño gráfico para redes sociales</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-pink-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i><span>Videos promocionales cortos</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-pink-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i><span>Fotografía de productos</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-pink-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i><span>Edición de video profesional</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-pink-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i><span>Banners y material publicitario</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-pink-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i><span>Infografías</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-pink-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i><span>Animaciones simples</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-pink-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i><span>Contenido para stories</span></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="p-3 rounded-xl bg-pink-100 dark:bg-pink-900/30 text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400">
              <i data-lucide="smartphone" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Formatos</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
                <li>• Posts para Instagram/Facebook</li>
                <li>• Videos para TikTok/Reels</li>
                <li>• Banners web</li>
                <li>• Material impreso</li>
                <li>• Presentaciones corporativas</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Herramientas</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-mono bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Photoshop</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-mono bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Illustrator</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-mono bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Premiere</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-mono bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">After Effects</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-mono bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Canva Pro</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-mono bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Figma</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-12">
        <button onclick="window.location.href='/#contact'" class="w-full py-4 px-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900 dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-slate-900 font-semibold hover:bg-indigo-600 dark:hover:bg-indigo-400 transition-colors">
          Solicitar Cotización
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">Preguntas Frecuentes</h3>
        
        <details class="group p-6 rounded-xl border bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
            ¿Por qué necesito esto?
            <i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"></i>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">La gente compra con los ojos. Fotos feas = no vendes. Videos y diseños profesionales hacen que tu negocio se vea serio y confiable.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="group p-6 rounded-xl border bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
            ¿Cuándo lo necesito?
            <i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"></i>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Para redes sociales, para tu página web, para publicidad. Siempre que necesites mostrar tu producto o servicio de forma atractiva.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="group p-6 rounded-xl border bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
            ¿Qué tipo de contenido hacen?
            <i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"></i>
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Fotos de productos, videos cortos para Instagram/TikTok, diseños para publicaciones, logos, flyers digitales. Todo lo visual.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</ServiceLayout>
